    "yg_image_with_text_list_KQztzz": {
      "type": "yg-image-with-text-list",
      "blocks": {
        "item_FQddzf": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/20260618172940_8568_790.jpg",
            "image_pos": "left",
            "title": "<p>1500W Peak Motor</p>",
            "content": "<p>With a 1500W peak brushless motor, 50N.m torque, up to 30MPH speed, and 30° slope capability, the GT30 delivers powerful acceleration, steady climbing support, and confident control for daily rides.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_Y77eFc": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/GT30_Folding_Fat_Tire_page_960Wh_Removable_Battery.jpg",
            "image_pos": "right",
            "title": "<p>Conquer Rough Terrain with Greater Comfort</p>",
            "content": "<p>The GT30 is equipped with multiple shock absorbers that help dampen bumps and reduce road vibration during everyday rides. Whether you are riding on city streets, gravel paths, uneven roads, or rough terrain, the suspension system helps provide a smoother, more comfortable, and more controlled riding experience.</p>",
